name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Start.photos - A beautiful+sfw new tab page

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple and sfw photo start page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Start.photos is a new tab page for people that want a beautiful start to every tab. A subtle clock is available, and most pictures present the photographic settings used by the photographer.

A start page with pretty pictures from around the web, with a privacy focus. No analytics data is collected, no product recommendations are provided.

Pictures are sourced from Unsplash and are hand-curated to be SFW (safe for work).
